                <li>Front-end: HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Angular, SASS</li>
                <li>Back-end: Node.js, Express, Python, Django, Ruby on Rails</li>
                <li>Databases: MySQL, MongoDB, PostgreSQL</li>
                <li>Tools: Docker, Git, Webpack, Jenkins</li>
                <li>Cloud: AWS, Google Cloud Platform, Heroku</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>Personal Strengths</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Creative problem-solving</li>
                <li>Strong collaboration and team leadership</li>
                <li>Effective communication skills</li>
                <li>Adaptability to evolving tech landscapes</li>
                <li>Attention to detail and commitment to excellence</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Beyond Coding</h3>
            <p>When I’m not in front of a screen, you can find me out hiking, exploring new cities, or experimenting
